MI AMORE chased the pace three wide and came up empty in the lane. CLEOPATRA'S NILE was bumped and shut off at the start and made little impact while racing three wide. ALCOHOL raced off the pace two wide between foes, checked near the five-sixteenths marker and had no further bids. REVOLU set the pace along the rail and retreated through the lane. TRANQUIL WATERS raced off the pace three wide, checked near the five-sixteenths pole and retreated.
